      "source": "https://grokipedia.com/page/kendale_lakes_florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 2024, Kendale Lakes hosts the last Kmart store in the continental U.S., a convenience‑store version of the big‑box chain.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        9,
        23,
        24
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
