    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Since the 1960s, waves of Cuban and Nicaraguan immigrants have turned Kendale Lakes into an ethnoburb where 86% of residents identify as Hispanic or Latino.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        13
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
